# Premium UI Enhancement — Last-Minute Life Saver

## Context

This is a **Vibe2Ship hackathon** project (PS1 — "Last-Minute Life Saver"), an AI-powered productivity companion built with:
- **Frontend**: React + Vite + Tailwind CSS v3 + shadcn/ui (New York style) + Framer Motion
- **Backend**: Express.js + Google Gemini 2.0 Flash API
- **Auth/DB**: Firebase Auth + Firestore (with demo mode fallback)
- **Deadline**: June 29, 2026 at 2:00 PM

The app already has a solid foundation with 7 pages (Login, Dashboard, TaskInput, AIChat, CalendarView, Analytics, Habits), a sidebar, topbar, and demo data store. The `ps2_analysis.html` confirms PS1 was chosen as the winning strategy due to its simpler scope and deeper AI integration.

## Goal

Elevate the UI from "good" to **jaw-dropping premium** — the kind of UI that makes judges say "I'd actually use this." We'll add rich micro-animations, glassmorphism effects, animated gradients, particle effects, and polish every surface.

